<refentry id="bif.ExePath" xreflabel="ExePath">

<refmeta>
<indexterm>
<primary>ExePath</primary>
</indexterm>

<refentrytitle>ExePath</refentrytitle>
<refmiscinfo>Built-in function</refmiscinfo>
</refmeta>

<refnamediv>
<refname>ExePath</refname>
<refpurpose>
Returns the path of the GCL executable
</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv>
<synopsis>
ExePath[{file->True}, {path->True}] =: TEXT 
</synopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsect1><title>Description</title>
<para>
<function>ExePath</function> returns the path of the GCL executable.
If <parameter>file</parameter> is <literal>True</literal>, the filename
is included.  If <parameter>path</parameter> is <literal>True</literal>,
the path to the executable is included.
</para>
</refsect1>

